title: Veeam Backup Repositories
agents: veeam_rest
catalog: app/veeam
license: GPLv2
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors Veeam backup repository capacity and status
 via the REST API.

 It reports:
 - Repository capacity and usage
 - Free space
 - Online/offline status
 - Outdated component warnings

 The check returns:
 - OK: Repository is online and within usage thresholds
 - WARN: Repository has outdated components or usage exceeds warning threshold
 - CRIT: Repository is offline or usage exceeds critical threshold
 - UNKNOWN: No data or repository not found

 Configurable thresholds for usage percentage and minimum free space.

item:
 The repository name

discovery:
 One service is created for each backup repository.
